Upon plate-based data acquisition using the Cellinsight exported data files, i.e. associated to the three parameters above, were uploaded to Scripps’ institutional database (Symyx Assay Explorer), where plate statistics (Z, Z′, S/B) were automatically calculated. Compound heredity was automatically retrieved from Scripps’ compound management database (Plate Manager, MDL), and percent neurotoxicity was calculated for each compound using the following equation:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
